'''Solomon Lamescus''' is a [[vampyre]] noble partially responsible for managing the [[Sanguinesti region]]. A prominent member of House Drakan, Solomon appeared in the 19th [[Postbag from the Hedge]] on behalf of [[Lord Drakan|Lord Lowerniel Vergidiyad Drakan]].{{CitePostbag|author=Solomon Lamescus|issue=19|letter=Letter 4}} He appears to be rather civil, and without intense cruelty (at least by vampyre standards), as he writes in a professional, while biased, manner.

